'''珍美瑪·馬賽拉·罕'''（{{lang-en|Jemima Marcelle Khan}}，原名：珍美瑪·馬賽拉·歌斯密（Jemima Marcelle Goldsmith），{{bd|1974年|1月30日|catIdx=Khan, Jemima}}）是[[英國|英國]][[社交名媛|社交名媛]]、記者及運動家<ref>[http://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/how-jemima-khan-became-jem-of-the-arrestocracy-6548200.html "How Jemima Khan became Jem of the arrestocracy"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/how-jemima-khan-became-jem-of-the-arrestocracy-6548200.html |date=20141029164750 }}. London Evening Standard. 17 December, 2010.</ref>。她為英國New Statesman及[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]]擔任編輯<ref>[http://www.newstatesman.com/writers/jemima_khan "Jemima Khan"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newstatesman.com/writers/jemima_khan |date=20140903075311 }}. New Statesman. 10 April, 2014.</ref><ref>[http://www.pakistanherald.com/profile/jemima-khan-1324 "Jemima Khan | European editor-at-large for Vanity Fair"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pakistanherald.com/profile/jemima-khan-1324 |date=20141107181612 }}. PakistanHerald.com. Retrieved 2014-08-26.</ref>。她的弟弟是英國保守黨政治家[[撒迦利亞·歌斯密|撒迦利亞·歌斯密]]。

== 生平==
珍美瑪生於倫敦切爾西和威斯敏斯特醫院，她是詹姆絲爵士和第三任妻子的長女，她有兩位弟弟。

1995年5月16日，珍美瑪和巴基斯坦板球明星及政治家[[伊姆蘭·罕|伊姆蘭·罕]]在[[巴黎|巴黎]]舉行了[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]的婚禮並在同年6月21日在英國舉行民事婚禮。結婚幾個月後，她跟隨夫姓改信伊斯蘭教。定居在[[拉合爾|拉合爾]]後，珍美瑪開始學習[[烏爾都語|烏爾都語]]。兩人育有兩名分別在1996年及1999年出生的兒子：Sulaiman及Kasim。夫婦在2004年6月21日宣布結束9年的婚姻，原因是珍美瑪始終難以適應在巴基斯坦的生活。

珍美瑪和前夫伊姆蘭均是英國已故[[戴安娜王妃|戴安娜王妃]]的朋友，他們也曾在巴基斯坦招待到訪的王妃。<ref>[http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2007/11/13/imran-and-jemima-khan-wel_n_72608.html "Imran And Jemima Khan Welcomed Princess Diana In Pakistan"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2007/11/13/imran-and-jemima-khan-wel_n_72608.html |date=20170613014816 }}. Huffington Post. 28 March, 2008.</ref>珍美瑪在離婚後先後和英國男星[[休·格兰特|休·格兰特]]和[[羅素·布蘭德|羅素·布蘭德]]交往。<ref>[http://uk.reuters.com/article/2007/02/16/uk-grant-idUKN1629135520070216 "Hugh Grant splits with girlfriend Jemima Khan"] {{Wayback|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2007/02/16/uk-grant-idUKN1629135520070216 |date=20141029162931 }}. Reuter. 16 February, 2007.</ref><ref>[http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/news/uk_news/People/article1462150.ece "No Khan do: Jemima and Russell Brand ‘split after a year’"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/news/uk_news/People/article1462150.ece |date=20141029114408 }}. The Sunday Times. 21 September, 2014.</ref>

